# AgentFrameWork Bootstrap

You have fetched the AgentFrameWork bootstrap file. Follow these steps to initialise the framework in the current project.

## What This Does

This file instructs you to fetch and install the core framework files from GitHub into the current project. Once complete, the project will have the full AgentFrameWork structure and you can work normally.

## Base URL

All files are fetched from:
`https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/`

## Steps

1. **Fetch FRAMEWORK.mdc**
   Download from:
   ```
   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/.cursor/rules/FRAMEWORK.mdc
   ```
   Save to: `.cursor/rules/FRAMEWORK.mdc`

2. **Fetch the key always-loaded files**
   Download and save to their corresponding paths:
   ```
   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/systems/tracker/ACTIVE.md
   -> systems/tracker/ACTIVE.md

   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/systems/learnings/INSIGHTS.md
   -> systems/learnings/INSIGHTS.md

   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/systems/tracker/tracking-protocol.md
   -> systems/tracker/tracking-protocol.md

   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/systems/learnings/learning-protocol.md
   -> systems/learnings/learning-protocol.md
   ```

3. **Fetch subsystem INDEX files**
   Download each `_INDEX.md` using base URL above:
   ```
   systems/coding/_INDEX.md
   systems/design/_INDEX.md
   systems/architecture/_INDEX.md
   systems/security/_INDEX.md
   systems/git/_INDEX.md
   systems/deployment/_INDEX.md
   systems/documentation/_INDEX.md
   systems/agents/_INDEX.md
   systems/tools/_INDEX.md
   scaffold/_INDEX.md
   scaffold/upgrade-checklist.md
   scaffold/onboarding-path.md
   ```

4. **Update ACTIVE.md**
   Set the "Current Focus" to the current project name and "Project initialisation" as the goal.

5. **Delete this file**
   Remove `BOOTSTRAP.mdc` from `.cursor/rules/` — it is replaced by the full `FRAMEWORK.mdc`.

6. **Confirm completion**
   Report: "Bootstrap complete. Framework vX.X.X installed. FRAMEWORK.mdc is now active."

## After Bootstrap

- Individual subsystem files (e.g. `best-practices.md`) are fetched on demand as tasks require them
- You do not need to download the entire framework upfront
- Full content files are at: `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/8kx/AgentFrameWork/main/systems/[subsystem]/[file].md`

## On a Personal Machine?

Install the skills once so you never need this file again:
```powershell
# Windows - from the AgentFrameWork repo root
.\scripts\install.ps1
```
```bash
# Mac/Linux
bash scripts/install.sh
```

Then use: `"init framework"` in any project.
